Summary for the code modification for spex bands and various gas densities.
2020/11/29 -MG

The following changes are based on the source code of SOS_Callable:

*Two files from SOS_Callable/src/pace_simulator are modified:
main_PACE_Simulator_DoubleK.f90=> main_PACE_Simulator_DoubleK_t2.f90
PACE_Instrument=> PACE_Instrument_SPEX_HARP_RSP.f90

SPEX wavelength and band width are specified in PACE_Instrument_SPEX_HARP_RSP.f90

*Makefile: makefile02_PACE_Simulator_DoubleK_SPEX_HARP_RSP

*Each gas colume density are scaled using a factor specified in the input file.

Input file example: spex_abs_scale.input
A template for the input file with gas name is provided: spex_abs_scalexx.template

